||AYSO soccer games||

Also located on the same block are ["Davis Senior High School"], The ["Veterans Memorial Building"], ["Davis Branch Library"], ["North Davis School" North Davis Elementary], ["Davis Art Center"]

There is a bike overpass connecting the park to the north Davis greenbelt that crosses over Covell. The park features two play areas ["Rainbow City"] and the Roundhouse. There are many fields for soccer and a softball backstop with concrete stands.
